SALESFORCE RELEASE NOTES
Craft Professional Quote Documents with Document Builder

Give your quote documents an enhanced and professional look by using the capabilities of Document Builder. Use the branding of documents, embedded images, document preview, and the PDF generation features, to ensure that your documents reflect your business goals and meet your customer needs.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Developer, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Revenue Lifecycle Management is enabled.

Who: This feature is available to users with the Document Builder User permission set.

How: To enable the feature, from Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Revenue Settings, and then select Revenue Settings. Turn on Document Builder.
To create quote document templates, from Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Document Builder, and then select Document Builder.
To view the document configured by using Document Builder, on the quotes record page, click Generate Document.
title: Enhance Quote Documents with Document Builder
